  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-04-13",
    "date": "2021-09-07T15:29:02Z",
    "text": "No Taxpayer Funding for Vaccine Passports Act of 2021\n\nThis bill prohibits the use of federal funds to develop a system that requires proof of an individual's COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) vaccination status as a condition of performing any action. If a state, territory, or locality implements such a system, it loses eligibility for specified COVID-19 relief funding."
  },
